Design System Guidelines for MMI Practice App

# Color System
- Primary: #635BFF
  - Main actions and focus states
  - Hover: 90% opacity (#635BFF/90)
  - Light backgrounds: 10% opacity (#635BFF/10)
  - Ultra light: 2% opacity (#635BFF/[0.02])
- Use text-[#635BFF] for primary colored text

# Typography Patterns
- Headings:
  - H1: text-xl font-bold text-gray-900
  - H2: text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900
  - H3: text-sm font-medium text-gray-900
- Body Text:
  - Primary: text-sm text-gray-900
  - Secondary: text-sm text-muted-foreground
  - Small: text-xs text-gray-500

# Component Patterns

## Containers
- Primary containers:
  - max-w-3xl mx-auto
  - bg-white rounded-3xl
  - border shadow-sm
  - p-8

- Cards:
  - rounded-xl border
  - p-3
  - transition-all duration-200
  - hover states: hover:border-gray-200 hover:shadow-sm hover:bg-gray-50/50
  - selected states: border-[#635BFF] bg-[#635BFF]/[0.02] ring-1 ring-[#635BFF]/10

## Buttons
- Primary:
  - bg-[#635BFF] hover:bg-[#635BFF]/90
  - text-white
  - rounded-lg
- CTAs:
  - Use rounded-full for main call-to-actions
  - w-full h-12 for large buttons
- Secondary:
  - variant="outline"
  - border-gray-200
  - text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700

## Icons
- Container sizes:
  - Standard: h-8 w-8
  - Large: h-10 w-10
- Always center icons: flex items-center justify-center
- Use bg-[#635BFF]/10 for icon backgrounds
- Icon sizes: h-4 w-4 (or h-5 w-5 for emphasis)

# Layout Guidelines
- Use space-y-4 for vertical stacking
- Use space-x-2 for horizontal spacing
- Flex patterns:
  - flex items-center justify-between for headers
  - flex items-center justify-center for centered content
- Grid patterns:
  - grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 for two-column layouts
  - Adjust cols- based on content needs

# Interactive Elements
- Transitions: transition-all duration-200
- Hover effects:
  - hover:bg-gray-50/50
  - hover:border-gray-200
  - hover:shadow-sm
- Selected states:
  - Use primary color with low opacity
  - Add subtle rings for focus states

# Effects & Decorative Elements
- Animations:
  - animate-fade-in for appearing elements
  - animate-float for floating effects
  - animate-pulse for loading states
- Shadows:
  - shadow-sm for subtle depth
  - shadow-lg for elevated components
- Backgrounds:
  - Use gradients: bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50
  - Glass effect: bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm

# Form Elements
- Groups: space-y-2
- Labels: text-sm font-medium text-gray-700
- Inputs: 
  - rounded-lg border-gray-300
  - focus:border-[#635BFF] focus:ring-[#635BFF]

# Modal Patterns
- Overlay: fixed inset-0 bg-black/25 backdrop-blur-sm
- Content:
  - centered positioning
  - max-w-md for standard width
  - rounded-xl with shadow-xl
  - p-6 padding

Remember:
- Always maintain consistent spacing and rounded corners
- Use transitions for interactive elements
- Maintain hierarchy with typography and spacing
- Keep components clean and minimal
- Use primary color sparingly for emphasis 